          hybridSearchArgs?: map[string]any(name='HybridSearchArgs', description='The algorithm parameters for multi-path recall. Currently supports RRF and Weight. HybridPathsSetting can specify recall of dense vectors (dense), sparse vectors (sparse), and full-text retrieval (fulltext). If the value is empty, dense vectors (dense) and full-text retrieval (fulltext) are recalled by default.

