*   RapidOCRLoader: .png, .jpg, .jpeg, and .bmp
*   UnstructuredFileLoader: .eml, .msg, .rst, .txt, .docx, .epub, .odt, .pptx, and .tsv
*   ADBPGLoader (free of charge for the first 3,000 pages): .pdf, .doc, .docx, .ppt, .pptx, .xls, .xlsx, .xlsm, .csv, .txt, .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .bmp, .gif, .md, .html, .epub, .mobi, and .rtf', example='PyMuPDFLoader'),
